videoSnippet.title: Never Play Passive, if Passive is not Your Style
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Hello everyone. Here is a fun game I played against a strong opponent. Hope you enjoy it. Time controls are 1:30 + 30sec increment.

Muhamed Borić vs Antonio Radić
Regional Croatia Cup, Cro; 2018-03-04
Torre Attack (A48)

1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 g6 3. Bg5 Ne4 4. Bh4 Bg7 5. e3 O-O 6. Bd3 d5 7. c4 c6 8. O-O Na6 9. cxd5 cxd5 10. Qb3 Qd6 11. Nc3 Nxc3 12. bxc3 e6 13. Rfc1 Nb8 14. Qb4 Qxb4 15. cxb4 f6 16. Bg3 Nc6 17. b5 Na5 18. Rc7 Rf7 19. Rac1 Rxc7 20. Rxc7 b6 21. Nd2 Bf8 22. h4 a6 23. a4 axb5 24. Bxb5 Bb4 25. Nf3 Ba6 26. Bd7 e5 27. dxe5 Bc4 28. Be6+ Kh8 29. exf6 Bc3 30. Ng5
